# Base URL for the API. Requests go through YARP gateway (see rms-aspnetcore-microservices).
# - Empty: use same origin; in dev Vite proxies /api to http://localhost:5000 (YARP). Order placement (POST /api/orders) is routed to Ordering microservice.
# - Set to gateway URL (e.g. http://localhost:5000 or https://api.yoursite.com) to call YARP directly.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
